description:
What are our responsibilities in preaching the gospel in the cities?

This is a #short clip from Pastor Mark Finley's message, "How Can We Effectively Bring the Message to the Cities?", and it
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h1wboSHTtD4 focuses on what we can do, with God's help, to spread the message of hope and salvation throughout the cities. Our responsibility is to go and fulfill the mission. God has promised to provide us with the strength, power, and authority we need to effectively bring the gospel to all of the people in the cities.


Watch the video to learn more about how we can effectively preach the gospel in cities where many people are seeking hope and salvation.
